Package de.axnsoftware.settings.impl.visitor

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IVisitor<T>
    The interface IVistor models a generic visitor used in building a hierarchy of IAccessorS from both annotated Classes and FieldS.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractFieldVisitorImpl
    The abstract class AbstractFieldVisitorImpl models the root of a hierarchy of derived implementation classes and it provides the default behaviour for all implementations of the IVisitor interface.
    ArrayFieldVisitorImpl
    The final class ArrayFieldVisitorImpl models a concrete implementation of the IVisitor interface that is responsible for visiting fields of type Array.
    FailFastVisitorImpl<T>
    The final class FailFastVisitorImpl models a concrete implementation of the IVisitor interface that acts as a sentinel.
    ListFieldVisitorImpl
    The final class ListFieldVisitorImpl models a concrete implementation of the IVisitor interface that is responsible for visiting fields of type List.
    MapFieldVisitorImpl
    The final class MapFieldVisitorImpl models a concrete implementation of the IVisitor interface that is responsible for visiting fields of type Map.
    PropertyClassFieldVisitorImpl
    The final class PropertyClassFieldVisitorImpl models a concrete implementation of the IVisitor interface that is responsible for visiting fields of custom type where the classes have been annotated using the PropertyClass annotation.
    PropertyClassVisitorImpl
    The final class AbstractFieldVisitorImpl models a concrete implementation of the IVisitor interface that is responsible for visiting classes that have been annotated with the PropertyClass annotation.
    SimpleTypeFieldVisitorImpl
    The final class SimpleTypeFieldVisitorImpl models a concrete implementation of the IVisitor interface that is responsible for visiting all simple typed fields, such as Integer or Enum typed fields.
    SimpleTypeVisitorImpl
    The final class AbstractFieldVisitorImpl models a concrete implementation of the IVisitor interface that is responsible for visiting classes that have been annotated with the PropertyClass annotation.
